message.text:
“𝑻𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒘𝒐 𝒈𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒕 𝒅𝒂𝒚𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒂 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏'𝒔 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 — 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒃𝒐𝒓𝒏 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓 𝒘𝒉𝒚." — 𝑾𝒊𝒍𝒍𝒊𝒂𝒎 𝑩𝒂𝒓𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒚

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends our heartfelt birthday greetings to the 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀 𝐏𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐫, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐳 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐨!

As we honor you today, we are reminded of the  profound difference one individual can make. We celebrate not only another year of your life, but the outstanding impact of your visionary leadership to our chapter, to our members, and to the community we serve. 

Wishing you a day full of joy and may this new year be filled with blessings, continued success, and all the fulfillment you truly deserve. 

Once again, happiest birthday, Ms. Maria Paz Alberto! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

message.text:
“𝑻𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒘𝒐 𝒈𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒕 𝒅𝒂𝒚𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒂 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏'𝒔 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 — 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒃𝒐𝒓𝒏 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓 𝒘𝒉𝒚." — 𝑾𝒊𝒍𝒍𝒊𝒂𝒎 𝑩𝒂𝒓𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒚

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends our heartfelt birthday greetings to the 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀 𝐏𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐫, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐳 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐨!

As we honor you today, we are reminded of the  profound difference one individual can make. We celebrate not only another year of your life, but the outstanding impact of your visionary leadership to our chapter, to our members, and to the community we serve. 

Wishing you a day full of joy and may this new year be filled with blessings, continued success, and all the fulfillment you truly deserve. 

Once again, happiest birthday, Ms. Maria Paz Alberto! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

message.text:
“𝑻𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒘𝒐 𝒈𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒕 𝒅𝒂𝒚𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒂 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏'𝒔 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 — 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒃𝒐𝒓𝒏 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓 𝒘𝒉𝒚." — 𝑾𝒊𝒍𝒍𝒊𝒂𝒎 𝑩𝒂𝒓𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒚

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends our heartfelt birthday greetings to the 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀 𝐏𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐫, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐳 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐨!

As we honor you today, we are reminded of the  profound difference one individual can make. We celebrate not only another year of your life, but the outstanding impact of your visionary leadership to our chapter, to our members, and to the community we serve. 

Wishing you a day full of joy and may this new year be filled with blessings, continued success, and all the fulfillment you truly deserve. 

Once again, happiest birthday, Ms. Maria Paz Alberto! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

message.text:
“𝑻𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒘𝒐 𝒈𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒕 𝒅𝒂𝒚𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒂 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏'𝒔 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 — 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒃𝒐𝒓𝒏 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓 𝒘𝒉𝒚." — 𝑾𝒊𝒍𝒍𝒊𝒂𝒎 𝑩𝒂𝒓𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒚

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends our heartfelt birthday greetings to the 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀 𝐏𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐫, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐳 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐨!

As we honor you today, we are reminded of the  profound difference one individual can make. We celebrate not only another year of your life, but the outstanding impact of your visionary leadership to our chapter, to our members, and to the community we serve. 

Wishing you a day full of joy and may this new year be filled with blessings, continued success, and all the fulfillment you truly deserve. 

Once again, happiest birthday, Ms. Maria Paz Alberto! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

message.text:
“𝑻𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒘𝒐 𝒈𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒕 𝒅𝒂𝒚𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒂 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏'𝒔 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 — 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒃𝒐𝒓𝒏 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒂𝒚 𝒘𝒆 𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓 𝒘𝒉𝒚." — 𝑾𝒊𝒍𝒍𝒊𝒂𝒎 𝑩𝒂𝒓𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒚

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends our heartfelt birthday greetings to the 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀 𝐏𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐫, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐳 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐨!

As we honor you today, we are reminded of the  profound difference one individual can make. We celebrate not only another year of your life, but the outstanding impact of your visionary leadership to our chapter, to our members, and to the community we serve. 

Wishing you a day full of joy and may this new year be filled with blessings, continued success, and all the fulfillment you truly deserve. 

Once again, happiest birthday, Ms. Maria Paz Alberto! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang
